  "texts": [
    "They posit that diversity is optimal when all topics are characterized by distinct top words.",
    "However, we question these diversity metrics because of the fact that certain topics naturally share the same words.",
    "For example, the word \"chip\" could be shared by the topics of \"potato chip\" and \"electronic chip\"; Similarly, the word \"apple\" may be covered by the topics of \"fruit\" and \"company\".",
    "This issue remains unresolved for reliable diversity evaluation.",
    "We in this paper propose a new diversity metric to address this issue (See details in Sect. 6)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}